721740f-a.title: Manhattan: Morton Street - West Street
721740f-a.text:
Morton Street, north side, east of and from West Street to and including Washington Street, showing the old one-story frame stable at 111 Morton Street, and the old Cyrus Rheims Stables at and adioining the N.W. corner of Washington Street. These will be demolished late in 1930 when the west side of Washington Street (q.v.)
is cleared.
May 112, 1927.
P. L. Sperr.
